a","tid":2183030,"uid":2546,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T22:37:35.000Z","msg":"同樣主一樣 兩年幾 無嗌過交<br />\n意見不合都係大家講出黎 大家退一步/協商<br />\n日日都話掛住要見面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樣主唔洗擔心 真係有呢類型情侶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (雖然以前都有諗過唔嗌交好似無乜經歷咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"7a259805bc995dec0612ac2eee15de10b1837acd","tid":2183030,"uid":357236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bef02c4107effcd9afbc1174bbacc831ecd3d2dc","tid":2183030,"uid":270438,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T17:12:28.000Z","msg":"識左一年 一齊左4個月<br />\n每個星期放假都會去佢屋企訓 晚晚都扑2 3次 訓醒又1次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 仲係好想成日見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:05:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">臭雞</span></strong></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c7065e1938e78ed0b0ac65503a74b8c2797b8933","tid":2183030,"uid":169116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:38:13.000Z","msg":"6個月"},{"pid":"2f4bcee63818022babfcb4939e60d6a9b3be5708","tid":2183030,"uid":144147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:29:51.000Z","msg":"一齊咗三年 三年嚟都冇鬧過交<br />\n可以話依然係熱戀期咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係日日見<br />\n但都仲係會每一日不斷喺tg傾計<br />\n傾下自己今日做咗乜 有乜得意野又講下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n偶爾夜晚會視像<br />\n仲係會成日好掛住大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算係嗰日先見完 分開咗一陣 又會好想見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁多年嚟都相處得好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}